    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227480/extras/cd3d6ab4fc36c11fb44354523168db92.avif?t=1725089365\" width=620 height=360 /></span><br><br><strong>Space Academy</strong> 是一款色彩缤纷的平台游戏，其中一名缺乏经验的飞行员准备踏上太空学院之旅，学习所有必要的技能。<br>进行一场激动人心的战役，揭开学院对新兵隐藏的所有秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227480/extras/8deeebb04a0889a4f6e3b0a4b6c4bce6.poster.avif?t=1725089365\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227480/extras/8deeebb04a0889a4f6e3b0a4b6c4bce6.webm?t=1725089365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227480/extras/8deeebb04a0889a4f6e3b0a4b6c4bce6.mp4?t=1725089365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>前往充满许多不同陷阱和障碍的学院。<br>平台游戏，您将在其中找到一切 - 困难的关卡、漂亮的极简主义 3D 图形、不寻常的角色、地牢等等。<br><br>接受挑战 - 通过所有级别并通过学院的一次期末考试。<br>但是我忘了说你没有任何超能力——你只是一个学院里的新手飞行员，有一个严格但经验丰富的中尉。祝你好运<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227480/extras/ff0da1e59040a3a5fbdc87bb133c3ad8.poster.avif?t=1725089365\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227480/extras/ff0da1e59040a3a5fbdc87bb133c3ad8.webm?t=1725089365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227480/extras/ff0da1e59040a3a5fbdc87bb133c3ad8.mp4?t=1725089365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>并体验随机生成的无尽模式，这将有助于您为学院的期末考试进行练习。<br><br><strong> 游戏特色:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 许多关卡充满了危险的陷阱和不同的机器<br></li><li> 对你能力的真正挑战<br></li><li> 漂亮的极简图形<br></li><li> 手柄支持</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\">